## 8. Slojevi primene

### 8.1 Baza (RLS)

Svaka admin tabela koristi `has_perm('<perm>')` po operaciji. Self-service tabele dodatno dozvoljavaju vlasniku pristup svojim redovima (`auth.uid() = user_id`).

**Mapiranje tabela → dozvola:**

| Tabela | SELECT | INSERT | UPDATE | DELETE |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `orders` | `orders.view` (+ self) | `orders.create` | `orders.update` | `orders.delete` |
| `order_items` | `orders.view` (+ self) | `orders.create` | `orders.update` **ILI** `orders.mark_pickup` (samo `pickup_status`) | `orders.delete` |
| `meals` | javno/auth (aktivni) + `meals.view` | `meals.write` | `meals.write` | `meals.delete` |
| `menus`, `menu_meals` | auth + `menus.view` | `menus.write` | `menus.write` | `menus.delete` |
| `menu_templates*` | auth | `menus.templates` | `menus.templates` | `menus.templates` |
| `profiles` | self **ILI** `users.view` | `users.create` (+ trigger) | self (zaštićeni `tag`/`company_id`) **ILI** `users.update` | `users.delete` |
| `feedback` | self **ILI** `feedback.view` | self | `feedback.process` | — |
| `suggestions` | self **ILI** `suggestions.view` | self | `suggestions.process` | — |
| `app_settings`, `kitchen_schedule*`, `meal_groups`, `allergens`, `companies` | auth/po potrebi | `settings.*` | `settings.*` | `settings.*` |
| `user_roles` | self **ILI** `users.view` | `service_role` | `service_role` | `service_role` |
| `roles`, `permissions`, `role_permissions` | auth | `service_role` | `service_role` | `service_role` |

**Storage:**
- Bucket „Slike obroka": **čitanje javno/auth** (zaposleni vide slike pri naručivanju), upis `meals.write`, brisanje `meals.delete`.
- Bucket „Resursi": `settings.organization`.

**Realtime (`realtime.messages`):**
- svi admin kanali → `has_perm('dashboard.view')`
- `kiosk-%` teme → `has_perm('orders.view')`
- `pickup_requests` teme → `has_perm('orders.view')`

> Pošto Demo ima sve write dozvole = false, RLS ga automatski blokira na svim mutacijama.

### 8.2 Edge funkcije

Obrazac:
1. `getCallerUser(req, adminClient)` — lokalno dekodira JWT (ne `auth.getUser(token)`, koji puca pod signing-keys runtime-om).
2. `assertPermission(client, userId, '<perm>', corsHeaders)` — 403 ako nema dozvolu (**fail-closed** i na grešku).
3. `assertNotDemo(client, userId, corsHeaders)` — 403 za Demo na destruktivnim/„slanje" akcijama (**fail-closed**).

| Funkcija | Dozvola |
|---|---|
| `create-user` | `users.create` |
| `delete-user` | `users.delete` |
| `manage-user-role` | `users.assign_role` |
| `manage-roles` | `settings.roles` |
| `send-invitation`, `send-magic-link` | `users.invite` |
| `update-user-email`, `reset-user-password` | `users.update` |
| `send-custom-broadcast` | `notifications.custom_email` |
| `notify-menu-ready` | `notifications.menu` |
| `send-employee-reminder` | `notifications.reminder` (+ sistemski/cron put) |
| `receipt-download` | vlasnik **ILI** `receipts.view_all` |
| `fiscalize-meal` (korisnička grana) | `orders.fiscalize` (kiosk grana = token) |

### 8.3 UI

- **`usePermissions()`** (`src/hooks/usePermissions.ts`) — učitava `get_user_permissions` / `get_user_panel` / `is_demo_user`. Vraća `{ has(perm), hasAny(...), panel, isDemo, loading }`. Dok se učitava → **pesimistično** (`has` vraća false), bez „admin vidi sve" fallback-a.
- **`<Can permission="orders.delete">…</Can>`** (`src/components/auth/Can.tsx`) — renderuje decu samo ako korisnik ima dozvolu.
- **Rutiranje panela:** `src/pages/Index.tsx` bira Admin/Employee panel preko `panel` iz `usePermissions` (izvedeno iz `get_user_panel`).
- **Ekran „Uloge i dozvole":** `src/components/admin/RolesPermissions.tsx` — lista uloga, „Dodaj ulogu", grupisani toggle-ovi, čuvanje preko `manage-roles`.
- **Read-only dijalozi:** ako uloga nema write dozvolu, dijalog izmene se i dalje **otvara za pregled**, ali su sva polja `disabled` i primarno dugme („Sačuvaj") sakriveno/onemogućeno. „Kreiranje novog" dugmad su potpuno sakrivena bez create dozvole.

